text:
Mumbai City FC vs Delhi Dynamos, ISL 2015 Free Live Streaming: Watch Free Live Stream and Telecast of Indian Super League on Star Sports, Hotstar and starsports.com By India.com Sports Desk on October 21, 2015 at 5:48 PM Comments 
Watch the Free Live Streaming and Telecast of Indian Super League 2015 (ISL 2015) Match 17 between Mumbai City FC vs Delhi Dynamos at the DY Patil Stadium . You can watch the live telecast of Mumbai City FC vs Delhi Dynamos match on Star Sports 1 & 2 and Star Sports 2 HD. You can also watch the Mumbai City FC vs Delhi Dynamos online via free live streaming by clicking on the live streaming link here . As for all the Hostar App users, the Live Streaming of the match can be found here 
Mumbai has been unlucky in this tournament. Nicolas Anelka’s men have terrorized defenses at times but have utterly wasteful up front. Sony Norde has easily been one of the best players to watch in these early parts of ISL 2015. For the ease at which the Haitian striker takes the ball past defenses, he does very little to get his name on the board in the goals tally. It was the same story in Mumbai’s previous encounter, which was a 0-2 loss against Chennaiyin FC. Also Read: Mumbai City FC Team Profile 
For a team that has so many good strikers in their ranks, getting goals on the board is an imperative. Nicolas Aneka has been restricted to barking out instructions from the touchline so far as he is nursing an injury. Mumbai though, will be galvanized by Sunil Chettri bolstering their ranks. The Indian skipper’s debut was a match to forget but showed glimpses of his class in the early stages of the game. Mumbai can learn a thing or two from Delhi to devise a winning formula.
